<li id="cite_note-7"><b><a href="#cite_ref-7" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFBogle2004"><a href="/wiki/John_Bogle" title="John Bogle">Bogle, John C.</a> (2004-04-13). <a href="http://www.vanguard.com/bogle_site/sp20040413.html" class="external text" title="http://www.vanguard.com/bogle_site/sp20040413.html" rel="nofollow">"As The Index Fund Moves from Heresy to Dogma . . . What More Do We Need To Know?"</a>. <i>The Gary M. Brinson Distinguished Lecture</i>. Bogle Financial Center<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.vanguard.com/bogle_site/sp20040413.html" class="external free" title="http://www.vanguard.com/bogle_site/sp20040413.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.vanguard.com/bogle_site/sp20040413.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-02-20</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=As+The+Index+Fund+Moves+from+Heresy+to+Dogma+.+.+.+What+More+Do+We+Need+To+Know%3F&amp;rft.atitle=The+Gary+M.+Brinson+Distinguished+Lecture&amp;rft.aulast=Bogle&amp;rft.aufirst=John+C.&amp;rft.au=Bogle%2C+John+C.&amp;rft.date=2004-04-13&amp;rft.pub=Bogle+Financial+Center&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vanguard.com%2Fbogle_site%2Fsp20040413.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Index_fund"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
